sequenceDiagram
actor User
participant Browser
participant View as SongView
participant FocusService as FocusModeService
participant Session as FocusSession

User->>Browser: Enable focus mode
Browser->>View: request focus mode
View->>FocusService: start_session(song)
FocusService->>Session: create session

User->>Browser: Next verse
Browser->>View: next()
View->>FocusService: get_next_verse()
FocusService->>Session: next()
Session-->>FocusService: current verse index
FocusService-->>View: verse content
View-->>Browser: render single verse
Browser-->>User: displays focused verse